Labels and Selectors:
=====================

- Standard method to group things together
- name the pods with the Labels
- select the pods with Labels
- Restrict nodes from accepting Pods
- Taint is set on the master to prevent any PODS from accessing the master node



Commands:
=========

kubectl taint nodes 

    - NoSchedule
    - PreferNoSchedule
    - NoExecute

kubectl taint nodes node1
kubectl describe node kubemaster | grep Taint


